Từ điển Anh - Việt
◘['ɑ:kitekt∫ə]
*danh từ
 ■thuật kiến trúc, khoa kiến trúc, khoa xây dựng
 ■công trình kiến trúc, công trình xây dựng; cấu trúc
 ■kiểu kiến trúc
 ■sự xây dựng

Anh - Anh
architecture
■ noun
1》 the art or practice of designing and constructing buildings.
    ⁃ the style in which a building is designed and constructed.
2》 the complex structure of something.
    ⁃ the conceptual structure and logical organization of a computer or computer-based system.
Derivatives
architecturaladjective
architecturallyadverb

Từ điển Đồng nghĩa
architecture
▸ noun
1modern architecture: BUILDING DESIGN, building style, planning, building, construction; formal architectonics. See lists.
2the architecture of a computer system: STRUCTURE, construction, organization, layout, design, build, anatomy, make-up; informal set-up.
